{"text": " QM format, it is a novel method designed to complement and enhance the core meditation program. It is composed of short, repetitive rounds of meditation training with short breaks in between. Through high repetitions you will train your ability to quickly enter the same and reproducible meditative state. It builds your capacity to systematically meditate on demand. When repeatable states are trained and reached at will, then you may practice meditation effectively anytime, anywhere.", "segments": [{"id": 0, "seek": 0, "start": 6.52, "end": 17.78, "text": " QM format, it is a novel method designed to complement and enhance the core meditation", "tokens": [50364, 1249, 44, 7877, 11, 309, 307, 257, 7613, 3170, 4761, 281, 17103, 293, 11985, 264, 4965, 12537, 51268], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2527689352268126, "compression_ratio": 1.3984375, "no_speech_prob": 0.10312118381261826, "words": [{"word": " QM", "start": 6.52, "end": 7.6, "probability": 0.5712887048721313}, {"word": " format,", "start": 7.6, "end": 8.26, "probability": 0.8882421851158142}, {"word": " it", "start": 8.84, "end": 10.94, "probability": 0.9403061270713806}, {"word": " is", "start": 10.94, "end": 11.1, "probability": 0.9945677518844604}, {"word": " a", "start": 11.1, "end": 11.24, "probability": 0.9860818386077881}, {"word": " novel", "start": 11.24, "end": 11.52, "probability": 0.9966153502464294}, {"word": " method", "start": 11.52, "end": 12.08, "probability": 0.9947287440299988}, {"word": " designed", "start": 12.08, "end": 13.68, "probability": 0.9797403216362}, {"word": " to", "start": 13.68, "end": 14.46, "probability": 0.9980892539024353}, {"word": " complement", "start": 14.46, "end": 15.06, "probability": 0.8188274502754211}, {"word": " and", "start": 15.06, "end": 15.98, "probability": 0.9938376545906067}, {"word": " enhance", "start": 15.98, "end": 16.7, "probability": 0.9989908337593079}, {"word": " the", "start": 16.7, "end": 17.12, "probability": 0.99615687131881